---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import myImage from "../assets/about.jpg";
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24" id="about">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Image Container - Takes 5 columns -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:sticky lg:top-24">
        <div class="relative mx-auto lg:mx-0">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
            <Image
              src={myImage}
              alt="Jake Meyers - Full Stack & AI Developer"
              class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute -z-10 -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl opacity-70 blur-2xl"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Text Container - Takes 7 columns -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
        <SectionTitle title="About" />
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Hi, I'm Jake Meyers, a seasoned full-stack developer and AI specialist based in St. Louis, Missouri. With years of professional development experience, I'm now offering freelance services to help businesses worldwide build modern web applications, integrate AI solutions, and create custom software that drives results.
          </p>
  
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">My Expertise</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Full-Stack Development:</strong> React, Next.js, Node.js, Java, TypeScript, PostgreSQL, MongoDB, and AWS cloud services.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Web Applications:</strong> From simple landing pages and business websites to complex web applications, utility tools, and custom dashboards.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">AI Solutions:</strong> RAG applications, chatbots, MCP servers, and intelligent automation systems with professional enterprise experience.
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>
  
          <p class="mt-8">
            With professional experience building enterprise-level applications in my day job, I bring that same level of quality and attention to detail to every freelance project. Whether you need a simple business website, a complex web application, a custom utility tool, or cutting-edge AI integration, I have the skills and experience to deliver.
          </p>
  
          <p class="mt-4">
            Based in St. Louis, Missouri, but working with clients worldwide, I offer the direct communication and personalized service that only comes from working with an experienced independent developer. No account managers, no bureaucracy—just skilled development and honest communication.
          </p>
  
          <p class="mt-4">
            I'm passionate about staying current with technology trends and can quickly master new frameworks and tools as needed for your project. From Java backend systems to React frontends, from simple websites to AI-powered applications—if it involves code, I can build it.
          </p>
  
          <div class="mt-12">
            
              <a href="#contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
            >
              Let's Work Together
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-5 h-5"
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>